data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET.  Step into this gorgeous and like new (2021), 1 level, 3 bedroom, 2 full bath, Craftsman style home. The open floor plan is smart, efficient, and ideal for entertaining family and friends. Totally MOVE IN READY, located in the highly sought after Wellington Subdivision, in the heart of Boiling Springs. The kitchen features granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and opens to the breakfast area, living room, and dining room. The Master Bedroom is located in the rear of the house, for privacy and a quiet retreat. The Master Bathroom offers a double sink, walk in shower, and a walk in closet. Don't wait and miss out on this house. Schedule your showing today. Located to all shopping, restaurant's hospitals, and I-85. ALL APPLIANCES IN THE KITCHEN, AND ALL WINDOW TREATMENTS CONVEY WITH THE HOUSE.
